''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' publishes annual lists of songs based on chart performance over the course of a year based on [[Nielsen Broadcast Data Systems]] and [[Nielsen SoundScan|SoundScan]] information. This is a list of the magazine's Top '''[[Billboard Hot 100|Hot 100]]''' songs of [[2008 in music|2008]].<ref>http://longboredsurfer.com/charts/2008.php</ref>
